name: One party and four public toilets
description:
It was going to be a Halloween event like any other, we planned it for months with my group of friends but a single visit to the bathroom of the bar was the trigger for an orgy to begin. 
Maybe the smell of the party plus the need for a ritual together predisposed us to embrace each other in spit and sweat. 
We are in for a long party that will last many days, whoever wants to join us is welcome to come.
